&lt;text x="520" y="393" font-size="20" font-family="Inter,Arial,sans-serif" font-weight="800" fill="#3730a3"&gt;Human evals&lt;/text&gt;
&lt;text x="520" y="424" font-size="15" font-family="Inter,Arial,sans-serif" fill="#475569"&gt;truth, policy, nuance&lt;/text&gt;
