&lt;text x="818" y="393" font-size="20" font-family="Inter,Arial,sans-serif" font-weight="800" fill="#991b1b"&gt;Production signals&lt;/text&gt;
&lt;text x="818" y="424" font-size="15" font-family="Inter,Arial,sans-serif" fill="#475569"&gt;corrections, retries, clicks&lt;/text&gt;
