&lt;a href="#sources-worth-reading" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2309.15217"target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;RAGAS paper&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="https://docs.ragas.io/"target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;RAGAS documentation&lt;/a&gt; for RAG-specific metrics.&lt;/li&gt;
